@startuml
title PU_01 Submit Inquiry - Activity

start
:Public User opens Submit Inquiry;
:Enter contact email and heardAboutUs;
:Include Use Case: Select Slot;

if (Slot reserved successfully?) then (Yes)
  :Submit inquiry;
  :Create DemoRequest in PENDING state;
  :Provision user account if needed (temporary password);
  :Send inquiry acknowledgement email;
  if (Admin review outcome?) then (Approved)
    :Confirm booking;
    :Mark slot used;
    stop
  else (Rejected)
    :Reject request;
    :Release slot;
    stop
  endif
else (No)
  :Show slot selection failure;
  stop
endif

@enduml
